Staying online should be safe and comfortable, whether you're working or just surfing the internet. For that, it is necessary to delete your browser history time after time. Firstly, this action makes it much harder for hackers to collect enough of your personal information to scam you. Secondly, over time a lot of unnecessary data gets piled up in your browser eventually making it slower.
